  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Post is in the buzzing centre of the village, the beautiful St Nicholas’ church and <a data-udi="umb://document/3a5143c480274e36b9af49fb9e370cf0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3a5143c480274e36b9af49fb9e370cf0}" title="Westendorf">Westendorf</a> square are just outside the hotel. Skiers and snowboarders can get to the nursery slopes and ski school in less than 5 minutes. More experienced skiers can use the chairlift on the nursery slope to access the main village gondola.</p>
<p>At Hotel Post you’ll notice traditional features in the original wing and a modern style of the newer wing where you’ll find a beautiful spa with sauna, steam room, whirlpool, infrared cabins and relaxation room- perfect for relaxing after a hard day’s skiing. The Hotel Post team work hard to make everyone feel at home here.</p>
<p>The hotel has a lively bar – you're just as likely to find yourself sitting next to one of the locals as a visiting skier. There is a dining room for guests on half-board and a-la-carte restaurant serving International and Austrian dishes in the cosy stube at the front of the hotel (Inghams guests choosing to eat at the a-la-carte restaurant receive a voucher in part-payment for their meal).</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Post the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
