  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>As the original village inn, Hotel Post is right in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/3a5143c480274e36b9af49fb9e370cf0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3a5143c480274e36b9af49fb9e370cf0}" title="Westendorf">Westendorf</a>. You’ll be first to the lifts, ski school and nursery slopes and have the shortest walk home after the laid back apres ski. The historic feel, welcoming atmosphere and great location make Hotel Post a great hotel for a skiing holiday.</p>]]></listingDescription>
